messages.subject: New Puppy
messages.msgSnippet: We just got a new puppy today.  The puppy is so cute and on the way home my youngest, Phillip, said something so cute.  The boys were sitting in the back seat
messages.messageBody:
We just got a new puppy today. The puppy is so cute and on the way home my
youngest, Phillip, said something so cute. The boys were sitting in the back
seat with the puppy on their laps. The puppy fell asleep and Phillip pipes
up....."Mom...we loved the puppy to sleep."
I thought that was so cute, had to share.
Pam G.
